CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: The St. Joe Co is a real estate development, asset management and operating company. The company owns 170,000 acres of land in Northwest Florida. The Bay-Walton Sector Plan originally included 110,500 acres of land, entitles, or gives legal rights to develop over 170,000 residential dwelling units, over 22 million square feet of retail, commercial and industrial space, and 3,000 hotel rooms on lands within Florida's Bay and Walton counties. Its operations are reported in three segments namely residential, hospitality and commercial.
